      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model is widely used but not validated specifically for rotating blood pump geometries at these Reynolds numbers. Power-law hemolysis exponents sourced from Giersiepen et al. (1990); known to produce systematic over-prediction. Model-form uncertainty acknowledged but not quantified. Achieved Gradation 2."
    },
